title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Sim update IV available!!
description:
Today Asobo released Sim Update IV right on time because it was already announced that it would release today. I am pretty impressed by the list of items being fixed in this Sim Update. Besides fixes the AIRAC data has been updated to version 2105.

In this video we will discuss the release notes and have a short look at the package manager changes.
